Package pfriendly

Interface IYupOgl

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IYup
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Up3, Yup2, Yup3, Zup3
    public interface IYupOgl
extends IYup
    An interface to maintain consistent behavior between OpenGL renderers, even when they are of different dimensions.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      static class  IYupOgl.Sampling
      An enumeration to make the texture sampling options available in Processing's OpenGL renderers (P2D and P3D) clearer.
